# {{project_name}}

{{project_name}} is a full-stack FastAPI project — a FastAPI + SQLModel + PostgreSQL backend and a React + TypeScript + Vite frontend, wired together with Docker Compose. It was scaffolded by [dev-ready](https://github.com/MoofonLi/dev-ready) on top of [fastapi/full-stack-fastapi-template](https://github.com/fastapi/full-stack-fastapi-template).

## Stack

- **Backend**: FastAPI, SQLModel, PostgreSQL, Pydantic — `backend/`
- **Frontend**: React, TypeScript, Vite — `frontend/`
- **Infra**: Docker Compose, Traefik reverse proxy — `compose.yml`

## Commands

- `docker compose up -d` — start the full stack (backend, frontend, database, proxy)
- `docker compose watch` — start with live reload for local development
- `docker compose down` — stop the stack
- Backend only: `cd backend && uv run fastapi dev app/main.py`
- Frontend only: `cd frontend && npm install && npm run dev`
- Backend tests: `cd backend && bash scripts/test.sh`

## Documentation

- Per-service setup lives in `backend/README.md` and `frontend/README.md`.
- `CLAUDE.md` — guidance for AI agents working in this repo (added by dev-ready).

